Uses of Class
de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.OpenInfraSchemas

  • Packages that use OpenInfraSchemas 
    Package Description
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db
    This package contains database related stuff which is required to bootstrap the database connections.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos
    This package implements all DAO classes which are used to access the JPA persistence layer (database).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.file
    This package contains the DAO classes of the file service.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.meta
    This package implements all DAO classes which are used to access the JPA persistence layer (database).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.daos.rbac
    This package contains DAO classes for role-based access control (rbac).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac
    This package contains classes of the role-based access control system (RBAC).
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.rbac.meta
    This package contains classes for role-based access control concerning meta data.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest
    This package provides classes used to produce the JSON and XML outputs for RESTful services related to both projects and system database schemas.
    de.btu.openinfra.backend.rest.project
    This package contains REST resources which exclusively refer to the project databases.
